  "identifier": "SB 2379",
  "title": "Firearms and Ammunition - As introduced, enacts the \"Reckless Bullet Prevention Act,\" which creates an offense of recklessly discharging a firearm into the air, ground, a body of water, or an object in close proximity to the person if the firearm is discharged at a place where other people are or may be present; punishes the offense as a Class A misdemeanor; specifies certain exceptions to the offense; requires handgun safety courses for enhanced handgun carry permits to instruct on the offense. - Amends TCA Title 39.",
